Professional Summary

Innovative game developer with extensive experience in Unreal Engine and Unity 3D, specializing in creating immersive gaming experiences through cutting-edge technology integration. My career has been defined by continuous exposure to emerging technologies, enabling me to maintain a consistent technological edge in the rapidly evolving digital landscape. I excel in collaborative environments, leveraging innovative problem-solving to drive projects from concept to completion. A self-taught AI technologist, I've pioneered the integration of generative AI and machine learning workflows into game development pipelines - from 3D concept generation and video-to-motion capture conversion to automated asset creation. My commitment to pushing interactive entertainment boundaries is matched by my ability to rapidly master and implement new technologies, ensuring I remain at the forefront of industry advancements while developing efficient AI-powered development workflows.
